'''過敏性休克'''（{{Lang-en|Anaphylaxis}}）反應係指一種嚴重的全身性[[過敏反應|過敏反應]]，發病極快且具有致命性<ref name="Samp2006">{{cite journal |author= Sampson HA, Muñoz-Furlong A, Campbell RL |title= Second symposium on the definition and management of anaphylaxis: summary report—Second National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Disease/Food Allergy and Anaphylaxis Network symposium |url= https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-allergy-and-clinical-immunology_2006-02_117_2/page/391 |journal= The Journal of Allergy and Clinical Immunology |volume= 117 |issue= 2 |pages= 391–7 |date= February 2006 |pmid= 16461139|doi= 10.1016/j.jaci.2005.12.1303|display-authors= etal}}</ref><ref name=Tint10>{{cite book |author= Tintinalli, Judith E. |title= Emergency Medicine: A Comprehensive Study Guide (Emergency Medicine (Tintinalli))|publisher= McGraw-Hill Companies |location= New York |year= 2010 |pages= 177–182 |isbn= 0-07-148480-9 |doi= |accessdate=}}</ref>。通常會伴隨以下症狀：起癢疹、舌頭或咽喉腫脹、[[呼吸困難|呼吸困難]]、嘔吐、頭暈及[[低血壓|低血壓]]；以上症狀往往會在數分鐘到數小時之間發作。<ref name=NIH2015/>

常見的引起過敏原因有被[[昆蟲叮咬|昆蟲叮咬]]、對食物過敏以及藥物過敏<!-- <ref name=NIH2015/> -->。其他可能的原因包含接觸[[乳膠|乳膠]]或運動<!-- <ref name=NIH2015/> --> ，有的病例甚至找不到明確誘發過敏的原因<ref name=NIH2015>{{cite web|title=Anaphylaxis|url=https://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/anaphylaxis/Pages/default.aspx|website=National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases|accessdate=4 February 2016|date=April 23, 2015|archive-date=2015-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150504041904/http://www.niaid.nih.gov/topics/anaphylaxis/Pages/default.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。過敏的機制可能是因為[[免疫|免疫]]性或非免疫性的原因，誘發特定某些[[白血球|白血球]]釋放介質<ref name="Khan112">{{cite journal|title=Pathophysiology of anaphylaxis|last=Khan|first=BQ|date=August 2011|journal=Current Opinion in Allergy and Clinical Immunology|issue=4|doi=10.1097/ACI.0b013e3283481ab6|volume=11|pages=319–25|pmid=21659865|author2=Kemp, SF}}</ref>。確診的方式是透過患者在接觸到潛在過敏原後顯露的症狀及病徵而定。<ref name=NIH2015/>

過敏性休克的第一線治療是[[靜脈注射|靜脈注射]]或[[肌肉注射|肌肉注射]][[腎上腺素|腎上腺素]]，並將患者置於復甦姿勢<ref name=NIH2015/><ref name=Review09>{{cite journal |author=Simons FE |title=Anaphylaxis: Recent advances in assessment and treatment |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-allergy-and-clinical-immunology_2009-10_124_4/page/625 |journal=The Journal of Allergy and Clinical Immunology |volume=124 |issue=4 |pages=625–36; quiz 637–8 |date=October 2009 |pmid=19815109 |doi=10.1016/j.jaci.2009.08.025}}</ref><!-- <ref name=NIH2015/> -->。此外，病人也可能需要注射追加的劑量。其他如[[抗組織胺|抗組織胺]]藥及[[皮質類固醇|皮質類固醇]]都屬於輔助用藥<!-- <ref name=NIH2015/> -->。有過敏性休克病史者，醫師會建議隨身攜帶[[腎上腺素自動注射器|腎上腺素自動注射器]]及記錄有自身病史的文件<ref name=NIH2015/>。

據估計，全球約有 0.05–2% 的人口會在人生某個時間點發生過敏性休克<!-- <ref name=World11/> -->，此比例似乎也在持續增加中<ref name=World11>{{cite journal|last= Simons|first= FE|author2= World Allergy, Organization|title= World Allergy Organization survey on global availability of essentials for the assessment and management of anaphylaxis by allergy-immunology specialists in health care settings|journal= Annals of Allergy, Asthma & Immunology|date= May 2010|volume= 1Ａㄙ04|issue= 5|pages= 405–12|pmid= 20486330|url= http://www.csaci.ca/include/files/WAO_Anaphylaxis_Guidelines_2011.pdf|doi= 10.1016/j.anai.2010.01.023|access-date= 2012-09-15|archive-date= 2012-04-26|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20120426002319/http://www.csaci.ca/include/files/WAO_Anaphylaxis_Guidelines_2011.pdf|dead-url= no}}</ref>。過敏性休克好發於年輕族群及女性<ref name=Review09/><ref name=CEA11>{{cite journal|last=Lee|first=JK|author2=Vadas, P|title=Anaphylaxis: mechanisms and management|journal=Clinical and Experimental Allergy|date=July 2011|volume=41|issue=7|pages=923–38|pmid=21668816|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2222.2011.03779.x}}</ref>。在美國，約有 0.3% 因過敏型休克求醫的患者最後宣告不治<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Ma|first1=L|last2=Danoff|first2=TM|last3=Borish|first3=L|title=Case fatality and population mortality associated with anaphylaxis in the United States.|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-allergy-and-clinical-immunology_2014-04_133_4/page/1075|journal=The Journal of allergy and clinical immunology|date=April 2014|volume=133|issue=4|pages=1075-83|pmid=24332862}}</ref>。過敏性休克的英文 (Anaphylaxis) 來自古希臘語的 " ἀνά (ana) "，意指抗拒，以及古希臘語的 "φύλαξις (phylaxis)"，意指保護作用。<ref>{{cite book|last1=Gylys|first1=Barbara|title=Medical Terminology Systems: A Body Systems Approach|date=2012|publisher=F.A. Davis|isbn=9780803639133|page=269|url=https://books.google.ca/books?id=cR5hAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA269|access-date=2017-12-15|archive-date=2016-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205065649/https://books.google.ca/books?id=cR5hAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA269|dead-url=no}}</ref>

